    Stay in the heart of Tokyo.
Open from June 2014, APA Hotel Hanzomon Hirakawacho is conveniently located within a 6-minute walk from 3 subway stations, including Hanzomon and Kojimachi stations. It offers free WiFi in all areas.

All compact rooms are fitted with a double bed with an original mattress optimizing weight distribution. A flat-screen TV and a desk are provided. The private bathroom comes with a bath tub and free toiletries.

Hanzomon Hirakawacho APA Hotel features drinks vending machines on site. A breakfast buffet is served at the on-site restaurant.

The hotel is an 8-minute subway ride to Shibuya and a 7-minute subway ride to Ginza area. Lively Shinjuku area is a 4-minute ride from JR Yotsuya Station, which is a 13-minute walk from the property. The nearest airport is Haneda International Airport, a 30-minute drive away from the property.

    Stay in the heart of New Delhi.
Just 1969 feet from Connaught Place, this hotel offers Wi-Fi accessible rooms with a flat-screen TV and DVD player. Located in New Delhi, it features an Indian restaurant and 24-hour room service.

Hotel Palace Heights is within 1.6 mi of Jama Masjid, India’s largest mosque and Red Fort, a UNESCO World Heritage Site. Indira Gandhi International Airport is 9.9 mi away.

Fitted with wooden flooring, modern air-conditioned rooms feature a full marble bathroom with a hairdryer. Coffee/tea making facilities and a fully stocked mini-bar are included.

Offering northern Indian dishes, the hotel’s fine dining restaurant, Zaffran, serves lunch and dinner.

Laundry and dry cleaning services are provided. On-site parking is free.

Featuring free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs in rooms, Hotel Corus is well-situated in the business hub of Connaught Place. Boasting a restaurant, it has a metro station at its doorstep.

Corus Hotel’s air-conditioned rooms feature modern dark wood furnishings and pleasant pastel colors. They are equipped with flat-screen satellite TVs, ironing facilities and a safe. Free tea/coffee making amenities are provided.

Hotel Corus has a tour desk that offers help with travel arrangements and ticketing. It has a business center and provides currency exchange and laundry services.

Bonsai restaurant serves a variety of Asian dishes in a cozy setting. Guests have the option of dining at the patio, which offers views of the grounds.

Corus New Delhi is 11 miles from Indira Gandhi International Airport and 550 yards from the New Delhi Train Station.

    Stay in the heart of New Delhi.
Featuring free Wi-Fi, Alka Classic is a heritage property which is just 1969 feet from the popular Jantar Mantar Observatory. It offers multiple dining options and free Wi-Fi.

Air-conditioned rooms feature cable TV, a refrigerator and tea/coffee making facilities. A safety deposit box and a desk are included. Select rooms also come with a private balcony.

Guests can relax in the garden and seek travel advice at the tour desk. The hotel also offers a 24-hour reception, a business center and a laundry service. Surang Coffee Shop features Indian and European food, while Vega Restaurant offers traditional vegetarian cuisine. Saqi Bar serves a variety of alcoholic and nonalcoholic beverages.

Located in the heart of New Delhi, Alka Classic Hotel is 10 minutes’ drive from India Gate, New Delhi Railway Station and the Red Fort. Rajiv Chowk is a 5-minute walk away. A 20-minute drive leads to Pragati Madian Exhibition Ground and Nizamuddin Railway Station. Indira Gandhi Airport is a 40-minute drive away.
